    <item>
      <title>01. freshPink</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/freshpink/posts/post-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/freshpink/posts/post-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;After enjoying several Hugo themes, I tried to develop a theme that suited my needs, refined it, and evolved it into this theme.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;While it&amp;rsquo;s simple and static page-based, the theme makes it easy to categorize your articles with tags and helps you manage your blog with multiple shortcut.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-getting-started&#34;&gt;1. Getting Started&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To begin using freshPink for your development blog, follow the installation and customization instructions available on our &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/your-repo/freshpink-hugo-theme&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub repository&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Dive into the world of blogging with a theme that&amp;rsquo;s as dynamic and vibrant as your ideas.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
